5d263c57286a33f566f5","tid":2450343,"uid":102387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},{"pid":"a6e13c1337d1f500d43a692f672b43755f57d957","tid":2450343,"uid":118880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icable.news/videos/921725368639644/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficable.news%2Fvideos%2F921725368639644%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d6dc90df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icable.news/videos/921725368639644/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又加速"},{"pid":"ddeea9b84d023817b40cc604126334ade35655a2","tid":2450343,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:08:29.000Z","msg":"二乜撚讀呀，今時今日使乜嘢法律呀，仲喺度扮立法"},{"pid":"ac649267e67a528f832beae5da06baac66edc204","tid":2450343,"uid":118880,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:09:10.000Z","msg":"【區議員宣誓】 【消息：當局最快本月底安排區議員宣誓】<br />\n【區議員宣誓】<br />\n【消息：當局最快本月底安排區議員宣誓】<br />\n涵蓋區議員宣誓的修例草案，提交立法會首讀、二讀。消息指當局預計草案一旦本月三讀通過，最快在月底能安排區議員宣誓。"},{"pid":"6dbe0dcae6c4f661a4320669130b54fdfaf62c46","tid":2450343,"uid":310005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"咁樣講啦 即係呢D區肯定DQ：<br />\n中西區：中環、觀龍<br />\n灣仔區：大坑<br />\n東區：太古城西、錦屏、丹拿、漁灣<br />\n南區：田灣、赤柱及石澳<br />\n油尖旺區：奧運<br />\n深水埗區：南昌東、又一村<br />\n黃大仙區：東美<br />\n觀塘區：協康<br />\n荃灣區：海濱、馬灣<br />\n屯門區：新墟<br />\n元朗區：北朗、嘉湖北、天恆<br />\n北區：石湖墟<br />\n西貢區：欣英、廣明、運亨(已辭職)<br />\n沙田區：瀝源<br />\n葵青區：石蔭"}]}